  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NavigationManager.Listener

    NavigationManager
    Deprecated. 
    As of SDK 2.1.1. See individual callback methods for alternatives.

    @Deprecated
public abstract static class NavigationManager.ListenerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements NavigationManager.Listener
    Default implementation for the NavigationManager.Listener interface. Users may use this abstract class and overload specific methods to have a smaller code footprint.
    See Also:
    NavigationManager.Listener
